column1: How many times have you come to this office for the same issue?
How much did you pay for transport to the service office?
How long did you wait in the queue before you were attended to?
Did you know before you came what documents you had to bring with you?
Did the staff you tell you their name or wear a name tag?
Did any official ask you for money or a favour in order to help you?
Are you aware that you can apply for a grant without an ID book?
Did the staff manage queues well?
Did the staff treat you respectfully?
What kind of grant did you come for?
Do you think that this service office will learn from this survey and improve their service?
